snippet.title: Among Us - Submerged Custom Map (Reveal Trailer)
snippet.description:
After months in the making, the first Among Us custom map is finally here!
Live on Twitch 8 AM PST June 25th! - https://www.twitch.tv/5uppp

Special thanks to:

Project Lead:
5up - https://www.twitch.tv/5uppp

Developers:
Alex - https://twitter.com/AlexejheroYTB
Rose - https://twitter.com/roobscoob1
probablyadnf - https://twitter.com/associatedlogos
Natsu - https://twitter.com/arctic_zeph

Map Design
Axyn - https://www.twitch.tv/axyn
Blaustoise - https://twitter.com/blaustoise

Artists:
theinkpages - https://www.instagram.com/theinkpages/
Cola - https://twitter.com/colerobin_
Flips - https://twitter.com/flipsonthemoon
Muji - https://twitter.com/mushrium
Xi - https://twitter.com/xiiyta
Sabi - https://twitter.com/sabimrtn
and everyone else who contributed to the Submerged Development!

edited by ► https://twitter.com/ashbisto
Sounds from Zapsplat.com & Epidemic Sound
#AmongUs #Submerged
